Title: Dragon Ball Z: Tree of Might
Writer: Akira Toriyama (original manga "Dragon Ball"), Takao Koyama (screenplay), Ward Perry (script conformation), Eric Vale (English script)
Actors: Masako Nozawa, Mayumi Tanaka, Tôru Furuya, Hirotaka Suzuoki
Plot: A group of aliens visit Earth to plant the Tree of Might, a plant that grants cosmic power by draining the Earth's life force.
